:: ===================================================
:: USER CONFIGURATION FILE
:: ===================================================

:: Absolute path for raw source media files
SOURCE=C:\batch-ffmpeg-smart-encoder

:: Absolute path for processed 720p outputs
DESTINATION=C:\batch-ffmpeg-smart-encoder

:: Maximum CPU threads allocated to FFmpeg
THREADS=0

:: Maximum auto-correction attempts per file
MAX_ATTEMPTS=3

:: Allowed duration difference in seconds between input and output files
TOLERANCE=2